                            </p>
                            <p>&nbsp;</p>
                            <p>
                                We may be a small business, but we’re fast and efficient.&nbsp;&nbsp;We work around the clock to get orders out as quickly as we can, because we know that nobody likes waiting too long
                                to get what they’ve ordered, so we do our best to ship every order as quickly as possible.&nbsp;&nbsp;
                            </p>
                            <p>&nbsp;</p>
                            <h4>Working Together</h4>
                            <p>Every shipment that leaves our store is a vote in favor of supporting cruelty-free options to make for a kinder world today and for the future!</p>
                            <p>Thank you for making us your supplier of vegan products, and if we can assist in any way just call or email and we’ll be here to help you!&nbsp;</p>
